{"tid":404961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［補選唯一選擇］大家點睇范國威？","createTime":"2017-09-18T13:12:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T13:26:40.000Z","uid":28938,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c235b5c649b143d75ee9b8ab3322ad8176c0b75","tid":404961,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:12:56.000Z","msg":"當年搞老大哥事件挑撥離間，再退出民主黨，雖然反骨，但由頭黎過搞新同盟都算有魄力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n立會議員最先出黎嗌本土口號，但做成點大家有眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同鄭家富反面，老實講鄭出黎𠝹票係事實，錯不在范<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n底下有班區議員離黨，直接搞到佢輸選舉，同佢平時黨內唯我獨尊又有好大關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近又反對劉小麗同長毛出返黎選，司馬昭之心路人皆見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢算係比較好既政客，勉勉強強啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢條友扮本土抽水，又反骨，好驚佢出賣港人"},{"pid":"bfa36b072b3f2a5622f04b5e5f44c64a6cf8516b","tid":404961,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:26:40.000Z","msg":"咁都負皮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}